{{Infobox company | name= Heliopolis Sporting Club HSC | logo= [[File:HSC logo.jpg|border|150px|center]] | type= Club | genre= Sports | foundation= January 1, 1910 | founder= [[Cairo Electric Railways and Heliopolis Oases Company]] | location_city= [[Heliopolis (Cairo suburb)|Heliopolis]], [[Cairo]] | location_country= Egypt | location= | key_people= Haroun El Touny <small>[[Chairman]]</small> Hatem Bashat <small>[[Vice Chairman]]</small> Emad El Messiry <small>[[Treasurer]]</small> | revenue= | operating_income = | net_income= | assets= | equity= | owner= | num_employees= | caption= | homepage= {{URL|http://www.heliopolisclub.com//}} | footnotes= | intl= }}
'''Heliopolis Sporting Club''' ('''HSC''', {{lang-ar|نادى هليوبوليس الرياضى}}, [[Arabic transliteration|transliteration]]: ''nādī heliopolis al-reyādī'') is one of Egypt's major sporting clubs.<ref>[https://www.panoramio.com/photo/6908898 Heliopolis Sporting Club], [[Panoramio]].</ref><ref>[http://www.facebook.com/pages/Heliopolis-Sporting-Club-HSC/24546039208 Heliopolis Sporting Club (H.S.C)], [[Facebook]].</ref>
== Club's history == Heliopolis Sporting Club was founded in [[Cairo]] on January 1, 1910, by the [[Cairo Electric Railways and Heliopolis Oases Company]], which managed the club until December 31, 1921. On January 1, 1922, the club members took over the management by a contract signed with the company.
The activities of the club included [[water polo]], [[swimming (sport)|swimming]], [[Diving (sport)|diving]], [[Squash (sport)|squash]], [[tennis]], [[golf]], [[Cricket (sport)|cricket]], [[field hockey|hockey]], [[Contract bridge|bridge]], [[bowling]], soccer, handball, basketball, Volleyball, Speed ball, Ballet, Gymnastics, Snooker, Athletics and different kinds of [[dancing]].
In 1947, the area of the club was reduced to its present size (around 19 [[feddans]]) after the company took back the land of the golf course. Golf was cancelled after the frequent objections of club members to the large expenses incurred by the game, which, after all, was not played by many members.
== Shorouk branch == Like other major sporting clubs in Egypt, Heliopolis Sporting Club has another branch, in [[Al Shorouk City, Cairo|Shorouk city]]. The total area of the Shorouk branch is three times bigger than the main club in [[Heliopolis (Cairo suburb)|Heliopolis]]. Thus, that area is more suitable for all developmental and improving future possibilities.
